---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import ServiceBlock from "../components/ServiceBlock.astro";
---

<Base
  title="t.bone — services"
  description="Software engineer. Technology enthusiast. Coding and spiffy sci-fi(ish) device stuff. I work alone mostly."
>
  <main>
    <div class="wrap">

      <!-- ── NAV ── -->
      <nav class="animate d1">
        <a href="https://tbone.dev">tbone.dev</a>
        <span class="nav-sep">/</span>
        <span class="nav-current">services</span>
      </nav>

      <!-- ── HEADER ── -->
      <header>
        <div class="header-prompt animate d1">
          <span class="prompt">$</span>
          <span class="path">~/tbone.dev</span>
          <span class="cmd">whoami</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="animate d2">
          t.bone
          <span class="cursor" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </h1>

        <p class="title-line animate d2">
          <span class="bracket">[</span>
          Software Engineer / Technology Enthusiast
          <span class="bracket">]</span>
          <span class="caveat"> if I had to give myself a title.</span>
        </p>

        <div class="intro animate d3">
          <p>
            I like to work with honesty, integrity, and at a steady (swift) speed.
            In the tech industry the title means next to nothing; trust me on that.
            Anyone who flaunts it has the mental condition I call <strong>"money brain" syndrome</strong>.
          </p>

          <p class="meta-note">
            // the meta hierarchy they don't tell you about:
          </p>

          <ol class="hierarchy">
            <li>a person with a good idea or vision <span class="dim">( or capital, sometimes, tbh )</span></li>
            <li>a manager — messenger between the bottom and the top</li>
            <li>
              an engineer — the builder — at the bottom of the barrel
              <span class="dim">...or down at the foundation, you could say</span>
            </li>
          </ol>

          <p class="tldr">
            <span class="label">TL;DR:</span>
            Coding, and spiffy sci-fi(ish) device stuff sometimes.
            I work alone mostly.
          </p>
        </div>
      </header>

      <hr />

      <!-- ── SERVICES ── -->
      <div class="services-header animate d4">
        <span class="hash">#</span>
        <h2>T.bone Private/Personal Tech Services</h2>
      </div>

      <!-- SERVICE 1: SECURITY -->
      <ServiceBlock
        heading="Technical Security Audits and Consulting"
        aside="not enterprise, but personal / private"
        delay="d4"
      >
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Phones</strong>
            <ul>
              <li>GrapheneOS flashing onto supported devices</li>
              <li>Non cell tower comms</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Computers</strong>
            <ul>
              <li>Linux can bring life to old systems</li>
              <li>Please get off Windows at least</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Home connected devices / networks</strong>
            <ul>
              <li>Wireless VLAN</li>
              <li>Mesh VPN <span class="dim">( personal VPN basically — not like Proton / Express )</span></li>
              <li>WireGuard tunnels + IDP</li>
              <li>DNS stuff</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ServiceBlock>

      <!-- SERVICE 2: CODE -->
      <ServiceBlock
        heading="Custom Code for CRMs, Web, and other stuff"
        delay="d5"
      >
        <ul>
          <li>Custom websites</li>
          <li>
            AI translator
            <span class="dim">
              — people send me ideas and I translate them into an image, data structure, or w/e
            </span>
          </li>
          <li>
            Custom plugins and connectors for a variety of apps / data sources
            <ul>
              <li>
                I've built a Salesforce org before <span class="dim">( solo, from scratch )</span>
                and have <strong>NO interest in doing that again</strong>
              </li>
              <li>More than happy to build small custom bits though</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </ServiceBlock>

      <!-- SERVICE 3: CRYPTO -->
      <ServiceBlock
        heading="Cryptocurrency stuff"
        aside="I don't have a token, or do that shady bizzyness"
        delay="d6"
      >
        <p class="note">
          <span class="bracket">[</span> buy btc — my only advice, tbh <span class="bracket">]</span>
        </p>

        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Crypto financial planning consulting</strong>
            <ul>
              <li>I manage accounts for a few people</li>
              <li>
                <span class="dim">NOTE: I prefer not to do this, tbh.</span>
                <div class="note">
                  yes, they still have their own private keys,
                  and don't need to ask me to retrieve their funds —
                  as it should be
                  <span class="dim">[ looking at you, mr. bank man ]</span>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>Teaching about hardware wallets, offline storage, and basic usage</li>
        </ul>
      </ServiceBlock>

      <hr />

      <!-- ── PRICING ── -->
      <section class="pricing animate d7">
        <div class="pricing-label">
          <span class="hash">---</span>
          a note on pricing
        </div>

        <div class="pricing-body">
          <p>
            I tailor cost to the scope of the project and the mission/purpose
            of what the individual is proposing to me.
          </p>

          <p>
            The type of website most businesses want can be created in about a week —
            even with a round of revisions or three.
            I won't charge you exorbitant fake fees for doing nothing every month.
          </p>

          <p class="dig">
            <span class="dim">
              ( SEO, and other weird words they choose to explain vaguely...
              you know the people I'm referring to )
            </span>
          </p>

          <p>
            My sites have keyword targeting, security, and internet standards <strong>by default</strong>.
            I don't require bloated software crippled with years of tech debt
            that needs a patchwork of plugins, add-ons, or integrations —
            w/e they call it with the thing you're most likely using.
          </p>

          <div class="hosting-fact">
            <span class="prompt">$</span>
            <span>
              I pay ~$10/mo to host a number of private apps and public websites
              split between two servers in a Dallas data center.
            </span>
          </div>

          <p>
            I charge for my expertise, not my ability to deliver a sales pitch.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ── CTA ── -->
      <section class="cta animate d8">
        <a href="mailto:hello@tbone.dev" class="cta-link">
          Holla if I can be of assistance
          <span class="cta-arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <span class="cta-sub">hello@tbone.dev</span>
      </section>

      <!-- ── FOOTER ── -->
      <footer>
        <span class="footer-left">
          <a href="https://tbone.dev">tbone.dev</a>
        </span>
        <span class="footer-sep">·</span>
        <span class="footer-right dim">built in astro · no wordpress was harmed</span>
      </footer>

    </div>
  </main>
</Base>

<style>
  main {
    padding: 3.5rem 0 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .nav-sep { color: var(--faint); }
  .nav-current { color: var(--muted); }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header { margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .header-prompt {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .prompt { color: var(--amber); }
  .path   { color: var(--muted); }
  .cmd    { color: var(--bright); }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--bright);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.15em;
  }

  .cursor {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 0.55em;
    height: 0.9em;
    background: var(--amber);
    margin-left: 0.05em;
    vertical-align: text-bottom;
    animation: blink 1.1s step-end infinite;
  }

  .title-line {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .bracket { color: var(--faint); }
  .caveat  { font-style: italic; }

  /* ── INTRO ── */
  .intro {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .intro p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .intro p strong {
    color: var(--bright);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .meta-note {
    font-size: 0.7rem !important;
    color: var(--muted) !important;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem !important;
  }

  /* numbered hierarchy */
  .hierarchy {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .hierarchy li {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 0.18rem 0 0.18rem 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    counter-increment: hier;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .hierarchy {
    counter-reset: hier;
  }

  .hierarchy li::before {
    content: counter(hier) '.';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
  }

  .hierarchy .dim {
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    display: block;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-style: italic;
    padding-top: 0.1rem;
  }

  .tldr {
    font-size: 0.8rem !important;
    color: var(--muted) !important;
    margin-top: 0.5rem !important;
  }

  .tldr .label {
    color: var(--amber);
    margin-right: 0.4rem;
  }

  /* ── SERVICES SECTION HEADING ── */
  .services-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
  }

  .services-header .hash {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .services-header h2 {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--bright);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  /* ── HELPERS used in body slots ── */
  .dim { color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; font-size: 0.85em; }

  /* ── PRICING ── */
  .pricing {
    margin: 0 0 3rem;
  }

  .pricing-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .pricing-label .hash {
    color: var(--faint);
    user-select: none;
  }

  .pricing-body p {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .pricing-body p strong {
    color: var(--bright);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .pricing-body .dig {
    font-size: 0.78rem !important;
    color: var(--muted) !important;
    margin-top: -0.25rem;
  }

  .hosting-fact {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: var(--dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .hosting-fact .prompt {
    color: var(--amber);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    padding-top: 0.05rem;
  }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .cta {
    margin: 3rem 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--amber);
    border: 1px solid rgba(200, 146, 42, 0.3);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 0.55rem 1rem;
    background: var(--amber-lo);
    transition: background 0.15s, border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .cta-link:hover {
    background: rgba(200, 146, 42, 0.14);
    border-color: rgba(200, 146, 42, 0.55);
    color: var(--amber);
  }

  .cta-arrow {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    transition: transform 0.15s;
  }

  .cta-link:hover .cta-arrow {
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  .cta-sub {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .footer-sep { color: var(--faint); }

  .footer-right.dim {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--faint);
  }
</style>
